quote.text: You may not control all the events that happen to you, but you can decide not to be reduced by them
quote.author: Maya Angelou

scripture.text: She is clothed with strength and dignity; she can laugh at the days to come

message:
Ms Sunshine ☀️

today might’ve been long, maybe even heavy or it might have been Amazing. But look at you ..you made it through with that same fire in your eyes. I see you, and I’m so proud.Whether you aced the day or crawled to the finish line, I’m cheering for you like you just won gold. You’re not just doing life Ms sunshine you’re conquering it and You are doing it gracefully.Take this moment to breathe. Smile. You’ve earned it. And remember, the world is better because you’re in it.Sleep easy, Queen. You’ve done enough for today. 💛,
